Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你期望怎樣的命運舞台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要什麼燃料
